title: Chi's Adventure (Sweet Home and New Address) Anime TV Series
description:
A total of 208 Episodes + 1 Extra
JAPANESE AUDIO
ENGLISH SUBTITLED
(If you have issues not seeing subs, must mean you need codec packs like k-lite or something similar. Same goes for other series that have softcoded subs)

It's actually titled Chi's Sweet Home (1st Season)
and
Chi's New Address (2nd Season)

but I'd like to call them both as Chi's Kitten Adventure.


Had it on my hard drive and thought it was funny and cute so releasing it back into the wild for people that love cats acting like cats.
